title: "Syn-APS: Universal Advanced Planning & Scheduling Platform"
message: "If you use Syn-APS in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - name: "Syn-APS Contributors"
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/syn-aps/syn-aps"
keywords:
