abstract: >-
  Syn-APS is an open-source, industry-agnostic Advanced Planning & Scheduling
  platform built on the MO-FJSP-SDST-ML-ARC canonical form. It provides a
  deterministic-first solver portfolio, universal data schema, AI advisory layer,
  and domain parametrization framework for any manufacturing, logistics,
  or resource-scheduling vertical.
